      <section eId="sec_CHC-827">
        <num>CHC 827</num>
        <heading>827.  Judgment of release from continued custody</heading>
        <subsection eId="CHC-827__subsec_A">
          <num>A.</num>
          <content>
            <p>The court authorizing a child's release from continued custody shall issue an order containing bail provisions, if any, and a statement of conditions imposed upon the child.  This order shall also set forth the date of the child's next court appearance.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="CHC-827__subsec_B">
          <num>B.</num>
          <content>
            <p>The court shall advise the child and his parents, guardian, or legal custodian of the child's duty to appear as well as of any conditions specified in the order.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="CHC-827__subsec_C">
          <num>C.</num>
          <content>
            <p>The child and his parent, guardian, or legal custodian shall sign the agreement of security and release and acknowledge the conditions of release imposed by the court.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
          <p>Source: https://www.legis.la.gov/legis/Law.aspx?d=73418</p>
        </authorialNote>
      </section>
